data.description: WELCOME HOME!  Brand new 2018 Manufactured Home with 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 1,976 living square feet and 0.54 acres in the SE subdivision of Lexington Estates in Ocala, Florida. Home features open living concept and a split bedroom floor plan with separate living and family rooms. Peaceful and quiet neighborhood. Carpet and vinyl flooring throughout. All bedrooms are a good size and have plenty of storage space in the walk in closets. The eat in kitchen also has plenty of cabinet and counter top space. The master bathroom has a soaking tub and a separate walk in shower. Inside laundry room. Lots of windows. Don't miss your chance to see this brand new manufactured home - schedule your showing today!
